Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.60,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\fs125\c&H65A5FF}托罗星云\N{\fs75\c&H65A5FF}463G区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:50.59,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}早上好  盖瑞  这是第1818天\N{\fs40\b0}Good morning, Gary. Day 1,818.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.36,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你能不能别这样？\N{\fs40\b0}How about freakin' no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这次比往常更狠了  HUE！\N{\fs40\b0}That was a bit harder than normal, HUE!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你好啊  我亲爱的朋友\N{\fs40\b0}Hello, dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}有段时间没见面了\N{\fs40\b0}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:27.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嘿！好极了！\N{\fs40\b0}Hey! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你怎么样  汉克？\N{\fs40\b0}What's up, Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嗯  是的\N{\fs40\b0}Hmm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.38,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}贝丝今天看起来很漂亮  看看她\N{\fs40\b0}Beth is looking good today. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.42,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}用她魅力四射的大眼睛凝望着我\N{\fs40\b0}Staring at me with those hot eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你  我... 一会见\N{\fs40\b0}You, me... later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}打牌吗  汉克？你想玩吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Cards, Hank? You want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我需要找个人和我打牌\N{\fs40\b0}I need somebody to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:49.13,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就决定是你了  啊！\N{\fs40\b0}So it's gonna be you. Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.74,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我的牌都被你烧光了  汉克\N{\fs40\b0}I'm starting to run out of decks, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嘿  盖瑞！你好啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Hey, Gary! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.44,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  饼干  好极了！\N{\fs40\b0}Ooh, cookie, yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.77,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哈！\N{\fs40\b0}Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.37,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE？\N{\fs40\b0}HUE?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.07,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}怎么了  盖瑞？\N{\fs40\b0}Yes, Gary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我可以拿一块饼干吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Can I have a cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.91,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嗯  不可以  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Mm, no, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.88,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}为啥不可以？你都给KVN打开了\N{\fs40\b0}Why not? You opened it for KVN.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那坨狗屎都不能吃饼干好嘛！\N{\fs40\b0}That sack of wet turds can't even eat cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他只是把饼干怼进处理器槽里而已\N{\fs40\b0}He just smashes it into his processor slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我恨KVN... 非常恨他  他简直是我生命里的祸根\N{\fs40\b0}I hate KVN... so painfully. He's the blight of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.62,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果你拿了一块饼干\N{\fs40\b0}If you take a cookie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.63,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我就不得不再给你加一天刑期了\N{\fs40\b0}I will be forced to add one full day to your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:29.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你觉得一天刑期  能吓倒一个舰长吗？\N{\fs40\b0}You think a full day scares the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:33.64,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  过去的五年里我每天都在和你解释\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, I've explained this to you every day for the past five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.67,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你不是舰长  你是这艘飞船上的囚犯\N{\fs40\b0}You are not the captain. You are a prisoner aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:40.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好像有那么一点点耳熟  现在  把柜门打开\N{\fs40\b0}Sounds vaguely familiar. Now, open this cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  它们真是太——好吃啦！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, they're just so-o-o-o good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嗯  嗯  嗯！\N{\fs40\b0}Mmm, mmm, mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊啊啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.92,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你的刑期增加了一天\N{\fs40\b0}One day has been added to your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦！我摸到了！舰长大人摸到了！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh! I touched one! The captain's touched one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}舰长日志80085\N{\fs40\b0}Captain's log 80085.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嗨  奎恩！猜猜是谁在找你！\N{\fs40\b0}Hey, Quinn! Guess who!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}还是我  盖瑞  奎恩  我考虑好了\N{\fs40\b0}It's me, Gary, again. Quinn, I've thought on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.47,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我决定  鉴于今天是个大日子\N{\fs40\b0}and I've decided that since this is a big day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是我们的纪念日  如你所知\N{\fs40\b0}the day of our anniversary, as you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是时候来点真的了\N{\fs40\b0}it's time to get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:10.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩  这是... 这是真实又纯粹的盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Quinn, this ... this is the real raw Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我过去一直没让你见到真实的盖瑞  现在我再也藏不下去了\N{\fs40\b0}It's been eating me up inside keeping the real raw Gary from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}五年以来  你的存在一直\N{\fs40\b0}For five years, real raw Gary hasn't been able
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在真实盖瑞的精神堡垒里挥之不去\N{\fs40\b0}to get you out of his mind fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在我见到你的那天  我就知道你是我爱的人了\N{\fs40\b0}When I met you that day, I knew you were it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}把我们的东西还回来  盖瑞！\N{\fs40\b0}Give us what's ours, Gary!
