Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.89,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 布鲁斯特恩博士  还有德瑞克！   - 减减肥吧！\N{\fs40\b0}- Dr. Bluesteen and Derek! - Lose some weight!
