Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}快点  德瑞克  跟紧！\N{\fs40\b0}Come on, Derek, keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.37,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们给了我一杯苏打水？\N{\fs40\b0}They gave me a seltzer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}为什么给我苏打水... 除非我点了一瓶\N{\fs40\b0}Why would they give me a seltzer... unless I ordered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我点了一瓶吗？是的  我点了！\N{\fs40\b0}Did I order it? Yes, I did!
