Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}真的没骗你  我没法再贴近你的脸了\N{\fs40\b0}Seriously, I can't get any closer to your face, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 那你的制服在哪  老兄？   - 我有制服  老弟\N{\fs40\b0}- Then where's your uniform, bud? - I have one, guy.
