Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我... 我落在厕所里了  狗带！\N{\fs40\b0}It's... in the bathroom. Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呀！\N{\fs40\b0}Shwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}看起来不错  盖瑞！\N{\fs40\b0}Looking good, Gary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.20,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你要把他扔在这吗\N{\fs40\b0}You're just gonna leave him in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.87,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你个... 你个混蛋\N{\fs40\b0}you chuck ... you chuck-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.74,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  亲爱的阿司匹林\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, sweet aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}三块钱  刚刚好！好极了！\N{\fs40\b0}Three dratnoids, exact change! Tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.55,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}走你！\N{\fs40\b0}Swallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:45.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你是个好人  盖瑞！\N{\fs40\b0}You're a good guy, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}天衣无... 呃！呃！\N{\fs40\b0}Now to be smooth as ... Uh! Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:56.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这可是第一次  我连招呼都没打  就拿到了一个女孩的电话\N{\fs40\b0}First time I got a girl's number before I even said "Hey."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.50,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}知道吗  我喜欢有很多电话号码的女孩\N{\fs40\b0}You see, I like that. I like a girl with a lot of phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}实际上  这是普朗克常数\N{\fs40\b0}Actually, this is the solution to an internal inconsistency
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.07,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}内部不一致性的解  此前从来没人研究出来这个\N{\fs40\b0}in Planck's constant that's never been solved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.77,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}因为至今都还没人发现这是个问题\N{\fs40\b0}because until now, no one realized it was a problem.
