Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - E-3559又是啥？   - 是那个\N{\fs40\b0}- What's an E-3559? - That.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 这个？   - 喵的就是那个！\N{\fs40\b0}- This? - Yes, freakin' that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那我可能真的起了个名字\N{\fs40\b0}I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你不知道那个是什么吧？\N{\fs40\b0}You don't know what that is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:39.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那可是个行星杀手\N{\fs40\b0}That is a planet-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你听到他说什么了吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Are you hearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这人居然说月饼是行星杀手！\N{\fs40\b0}Freakin' guy thinks Mooncake is a planet-killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:48.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这都哪跟哪啊... 我的老天哪！\N{\fs40\b0}What a freakin' ... oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你给我闭嘴  KVN！智障   - 你觉得这很好玩？\N{\fs40\b0}- Shut your face hole, KVN! Crap. - So you think this is funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我很严肃   - 你很严肃？\N{\fs40\b0}- I'm serious. - Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:57.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是的  总司令满银河地找它\N{\fs40\b0}Yes. The Lord Commander is searching the galaxy for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你藏不住的  无论你去哪  他都会找到你\N{\fs40\b0}You can't hide. Wherever you go, he'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我为什么要相信你  胡子先生？\N{\fs40\b0}Why should I believe you, Mr. Whiskers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}再叫我一遍这个名字  我就杀了你\N{\fs40\b0}Call me that again, and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嗯嗯  我还冒犯你了  实际上\N{\fs40\b0}Mm-hmm. I've insulted you. You see, the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我从来没和猫人打过交道\N{\fs40\b0}I've never socialized with a cat man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.79,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我邻居有只猫  很喜欢舔自己\N{\fs40\b0}My neighbor had a cat. Loved to lick himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.16,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你不会舔自己吧？不会吧？\N{\fs40\b0}You're not gonna do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不然  我们之间就有问题了  朋友\N{\fs40\b0}Otherwise, we're gonna have problems, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我不是猫  我是文特里西人\N{\fs40\b0}I'm not a cat, I'm a Ventrexian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.47,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我知道了  我还是个长老派教徒呢\N{\fs40\b0}Got it. See, I'm a Presbyterian myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}但我爱所有人\N{\fs40\b0}But I love all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我从小受到的教育就是这样的   - 我们有麻烦了\N{\fs40\b0}- Just how I was raised. - We're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.71,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}听着  我们都有麻烦了！\N{\fs40\b0}Listen, all of us are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}月饼  看看盖瑞圆圆的眼珠\N{\fs40\b0}Mooncake, look into Gary's gelatinous marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}只要我还有一口气\N{\fs40\b0}As long as I draw breath and you provide me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}只要你还能给我带来无尽的冒险\N{\fs40\b0}with copious amounts of adventure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:38.82,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我就会一直陪着你  我们是一个团队\N{\fs40\b0}I will be there for you. We're a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会让你当我的好朋友\N{\fs40\b0}And I'll let you be my sidekick and such
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.12,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我也会成为你的好朋友\N{\fs40\b0}with a super side order of what-not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.46,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}说得好\N{\fs40\b0}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:47.79,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一块饼干... 这是给我的？！\N{\fs40\b0}A cookie ... for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.73,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是的  盖瑞  拿一块吧\N{\fs40\b0}Yes, Gary. Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.97,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你展现出了一种我之前没在你身上见过的品质\N{\fs40\b0}You displayed a quality I hadn't seen in you previously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.84,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}勇气  堪称典范的勇气  你配的上拿一块\N{\fs40\b0}courage. Exemplary. You earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.17,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我能拿饼干  还因为我是舰长大人啊！\N{\fs40\b0}And because I am the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.34,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}饼干收回了\N{\fs40\b0}Cookie withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}悔悟之人必得原谅\N{\fs40\b0}The penitent man shall pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦！我拿到了！\N{\fs40\b0}Ohh! I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:11.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}格兰多的手套啊  我拿到了一块饼干！\N{\fs40\b0}Sweet Grandor's glove, I got a mother-loving cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.25,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这是一块饼干  奎恩\N{\fs40\b0}This is a cookie, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.92,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE说这是我自己挣来的  因为我做了大事  奎恩\N{\fs40\b0}HUE said I earned it because I did things, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.87,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}危险的事\N{\fs40\b0}Dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}值得赢得饼干的事\N{\fs40\b0}Cookie-earning things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:23.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}现在  我要吃掉我光荣的成果了\N{\fs40\b0}Now to eat the fruits of my greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 是我的了！   - 啥？不要！\N{\fs40\b0}- Mine! - What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}KVN！哦  KVN！\N{\fs40\b0}KVN! Oh, KVN!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:37.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞？盖瑞？盖瑞？！\N{\fs40\b0}Gary? Gary? Gary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:40.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞？盖瑞  盖瑞！\N{\fs40\b0}Gary? Gary. Gary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  你在睡吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.12,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Wah-pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:45.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  好的好的  我们... 我们很好  别理我\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, okay. We... we're good. Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我... 我这就往这边走\N{\fs40\b0}I'm ... I'm just floating this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这边是我想走的路\N{\fs40\b0}This is the way I like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}拜拜！这是我的想法  这是我的道路\N{\fs40\b0}Bye! This was my plan. That's my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:08.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所有棋子都就位了\N{\fs40\b0}All the pieces are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.55,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}让我陪你玩一会吧\N{\fs40\b0}Let's play a little.
